WEBVTT

00:13.248 --> 00:16.384
(Lishan Mountain)

00:35.456 --> 00:37.664
(Lishan Academy)

01:01.640 --> 01:02.920
Ye Li

01:03.104 --> 01:04.719
has been ill since her return.

01:05.120 --> 01:07.319
Life in the mountains
must have been hard.

01:08.439 --> 01:09.599
On top of that,

01:09.879 --> 01:11.879
she was supposed to marry Prince Li.

01:11.879 --> 01:13.439
But with the swap,

01:13.439 --> 01:15.120
she's marrying the disabled Prince Ding.

01:16.560 --> 01:18.319
Lishan Academy may be a fine place,

01:18.439 --> 01:20.000
but it's no match for the capital.

01:21.519 --> 01:23.439
(Ye Li, daughter of second branch)
To think the peerless Prince Li

01:23.719 --> 01:25.040
and the crippled Prince Ding

01:25.239 --> 01:26.799
are holding weddings on the same day.

01:40.159 --> 01:41.760
(Time loses meaning in the mountains.)

01:42.680 --> 01:44.239
(The passing of years goes unnoticed.)

01:45.959 --> 01:47.239
(Eight years have passed.)

01:47.936 --> 01:48.959
(The good thing is,)

01:49.824 --> 01:51.159
(I've returned.)

01:58.528 --> 02:05.120
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

02:08.704 --> 02:14.848
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

02:17.056 --> 02:20.288
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

02:20.512 --> 02:26.528
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

02:26.848 --> 02:30.272
♪To the horizon's call♪

02:30.336 --> 02:36.896
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

02:37.952 --> 02:41.888
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

02:41.888 --> 02:47.968
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

02:48.256 --> 02:52.128
♪Put every twist behind you♪

02:52.128 --> 02:56.992
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

02:57.376 --> 03:00.096
♪Make headway against the wind♪

03:00.096 --> 03:03.083
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

03:03.136 --> 03:08.544
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

03:09.056 --> 03:12.995
♪Let your nature burst free♪

03:14.656 --> 03:19.648
=The First Jasmine=

03:19.776 --> 03:22.417
=Episode 1=

03:24.840 --> 03:25.439
My Lady.

03:26.560 --> 03:28.719
My Lady, how are you feeling today?

03:29.120 --> 03:29.719
Better.

03:30.400 --> 03:31.840
I just picked up the medicine.

03:32.039 --> 03:34.240
Xing, prepare the medicine for our lady.

03:35.039 --> 03:36.439
With cold water or hot?

03:37.400 --> 03:39.599
She's clueless. Give it to me.

03:39.879 --> 03:40.919
Thank you, ma'am.

03:41.319 --> 03:42.280
Come with me

03:42.280 --> 03:44.520
to bring our lady her lunch.

03:53.520 --> 03:54.879
When did it fly back?

03:56.639 --> 03:57.400
It must be hungry.

04:15.039 --> 04:15.840
Qingyu.

04:16.040 --> 04:18.360
What was all the fuss about
at Yanru Pond?

04:18.519 --> 04:20.879
(Qingyu, Xing)
Young Master accidentally fell in.

04:20.879 --> 04:22.199
Everyone rushed over.

04:22.199 --> 04:24.279
Fortunately, they got him out in time.

04:24.800 --> 04:25.376
Right.

04:26.120 --> 04:27.079
And I heard

04:27.079 --> 04:29.959
the plaque bestowed by the late Emperor
was missing.

04:30.319 --> 04:32.519
The one in the grand hall

04:32.680 --> 04:35.800
that reads "Family of Charity".

04:38.120 --> 04:39.040
That is missing?

04:42.439 --> 04:43.240
It's terrible.

04:43.424 --> 04:45.399
(Happiness)

04:45.399 --> 04:47.480
Rong, are you hurt anywhere?

04:47.600 --> 04:49.040
I-I'm scared.

04:49.759 --> 04:52.439
Mom, hold me.

04:52.439 --> 04:53.639
Come here, my child.

04:53.800 --> 04:55.720
Master Wending, Elders,

04:56.319 --> 04:58.360
when I came to clean at noon,

04:58.360 --> 04:59.800
the plaque was there.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.519
(Ye Wending, first branch)
Then Young Master fell into the pond.

05:01.879 --> 05:03.639
So we hurried over to save him.

05:04.079 --> 05:07.000
When we returned, the plaque was gone.

05:07.000 --> 05:07.240
(Ye Wenhua, second branch)

05:07.240 --> 05:09.519
It all happened within half an hour.

05:09.920 --> 05:11.279
In half an hour?

05:12.879 --> 05:14.279
How did such a huge plaque

05:14.839 --> 05:16.319
vanish into thin air?

05:16.639 --> 05:17.279
An inside job.

05:17.279 --> 05:17.920
(Ye Wenshen, third branch)

05:17.920 --> 05:19.120
An inside job for sure.

05:19.120 --> 05:21.759
Since the thief
managed to infiltrate us,

05:21.839 --> 05:23.360
why steal a plaque

05:23.439 --> 05:25.399
instead of anything else?

05:26.040 --> 05:28.319
Wending, isn't it obvious?

05:28.720 --> 05:30.800
Someone is displeased with us,

05:30.959 --> 05:32.079
thinking we don't deserve

05:32.079 --> 05:34.120
the title "Family of Charity."

05:34.279 --> 05:35.399
They're upholding justice

05:35.399 --> 05:37.759
by taking this plaque back
for the late Emperor.

05:37.759 --> 05:39.160
Just keep quiet.

05:39.839 --> 05:40.879
Enough talk.

05:41.160 --> 05:42.519
Our top priority now

05:42.519 --> 05:44.800
is to locate the plaque.

05:45.279 --> 05:47.920
How can we lose an imperial gift?

05:47.959 --> 05:50.399
Wending, what is on your mind?

05:50.759 --> 05:51.560
Think about it.

05:52.480 --> 05:54.600
If someone tried to smuggle

05:54.600 --> 05:55.904
such a huge plaque out,

05:55.904 --> 05:57.879
it couldn't possibly go unnoticed.

06:06.399 --> 06:08.279
Perhaps, the plaque

06:08.519 --> 06:11.879
is hidden somewhere within the mansion.

06:13.279 --> 06:13.920
Guards.

06:17.856 --> 06:18.800
Master Wending.

06:19.160 --> 06:21.279
Search the entire mansion.

06:21.439 --> 06:24.120
Leave no stone unturned.

06:24.120 --> 06:24.920
(Li Feibai)
Yes, Master.

06:26.176 --> 06:27.806
(Ye Rong, young son of second branch)

06:27.806 --> 06:29.280
(Ms. Wang,
subsequent wife of second branch)

06:31.040 --> 06:31.560
Nothing here.

06:33.920 --> 06:34.519
Over there.

06:35.360 --> 06:36.000
Yes.

06:40.600 --> 06:41.519
Nothing, Captain Li.

06:42.240 --> 06:43.160
Nothing, Captain Li.

06:43.279 --> 06:44.439
Nothing, Captain Li.

06:44.736 --> 06:45.920
Search the Western Courtyard.

06:45.920 --> 06:47.399
- Yes, Captain.
- Yes, Captain.

06:47.399 --> 06:48.759
We need to inspect these chests.

06:48.759 --> 06:49.639
You can't open them.

06:49.839 --> 06:50.519
Step aside.

06:50.680 --> 06:52.759
These are our lady's dowries.

06:52.759 --> 06:53.639
You can't open them.

06:56.800 --> 06:58.920
We're searching for a lost item
under command.

06:59.264 --> 06:59.959
Open them.

07:00.600 --> 07:01.560
- You can't.
- Wait.

07:03.199 --> 07:03.920
My Lady.

07:04.600 --> 07:06.680
You just took your medicine.
Why did you come out?

07:08.439 --> 07:09.519
Something is missing.

07:09.959 --> 07:11.720
I know you're just following orders.

07:12.680 --> 07:13.680
But these

07:13.680 --> 07:15.680
are the dowries my mom left for me.

07:16.040 --> 07:17.560
I don't have the keys right now.

07:18.160 --> 07:20.920
Forcing the chests open
might damage the items.

07:25.639 --> 07:26.720
Who sent you?

07:28.000 --> 07:28.839
Master Wending.

07:31.879 --> 07:33.560
Take me to Uncle Wending.

07:36.320 --> 07:40.416
(Rongxi Hall)

07:44.320 --> 07:46.272
(Ye Ying,
second daughter of second branch)

07:49.360 --> 07:50.080
My dear niece.

07:50.912 --> 07:52.680
Didn't you ask to come here?

07:53.079 --> 07:54.920
Speak your mind.

08:06.680 --> 08:08.000
May you be well, Father.

08:15.120 --> 08:16.160
It's been eight years.

08:17.040 --> 08:18.480
You've lost so much weight.

08:23.240 --> 08:25.160
Haven't you been back
for over two months?

08:25.279 --> 08:26.879
You still haven't seen your father?

08:26.959 --> 08:28.600
Father must have been too busy with work

08:29.079 --> 08:30.079
to see me.

08:35.320 --> 08:36.159
What a caring father

08:37.159 --> 08:38.439
and a filial daughter.

08:38.880 --> 08:40.240
I truly envy you.

08:43.000 --> 08:44.440
Something is missing.

08:44.519 --> 08:46.159
We must find it as soon as possible.

08:46.519 --> 08:48.840
Li, show some understanding.

08:50.919 --> 08:51.679
Uncle.

08:53.120 --> 08:55.159
I know the bestowed plaque is missing.

08:55.679 --> 08:56.919
I don't mean to stop you.

08:57.320 --> 09:00.399
But these are the dowries
my mom left for me.

09:00.679 --> 09:01.679
I don't have the keys.

09:02.720 --> 09:03.720
All these years,

09:04.360 --> 09:06.720
Mother has been keeping them for me.

09:12.320 --> 09:12.960
Yes.

09:13.639 --> 09:14.960
I have the keys.

09:15.840 --> 09:18.639
Li's mom prepared these dowries

09:18.639 --> 09:20.544
to take to the groom's family

09:20.544 --> 09:21.679
on her wedding day.

09:22.112 --> 09:24.480
Opening the chests early
would bring bad luck.

09:25.320 --> 09:26.200
Bad luck?

09:28.200 --> 09:29.879
If we don't find the plaque,

09:30.279 --> 09:33.200
the entire Ye family
will be in grave trouble.

09:33.279 --> 09:34.360
But that plaque is huge.

09:34.360 --> 09:36.240
It won't fit inside a dowry chest.

09:36.240 --> 09:38.759
Says who? I think it fits in this one.

09:39.399 --> 09:41.000
Right, Li? Let's measure it.

09:41.792 --> 09:43.039
(Duyou Zither)

09:43.039 --> 09:45.840
This is the Duyou Zither,
three chi and five cun long.

09:46.159 --> 09:48.320
It took Master Su seven years to craft.

09:48.960 --> 09:51.320
The imperial plaque
is about four chi long.

09:51.639 --> 09:53.840
The chest is big enough for that.

09:54.960 --> 09:56.480
I told you it could fit.

09:57.360 --> 09:59.519
Where's the key? Open it now.

10:05.200 --> 10:06.639
Stop hesitating. The keys.

10:06.639 --> 10:07.480
Wenhua.

10:07.600 --> 10:09.080
Give them to her.

10:25.399 --> 10:27.480
This is the Duyou Zither?

10:28.519 --> 10:29.240
How can it be?

10:34.600 --> 10:37.720
This zither looks like
that of a northerner.

10:41.240 --> 10:41.919
Go ahead.

10:53.120 --> 10:55.600
This is wrong. These are all wrong.

10:59.960 --> 11:00.832
Father.

11:01.376 --> 11:03.080
Do you truly detest me so deeply

11:03.360 --> 11:04.850
that you have to take the dowries

11:04.850 --> 11:06.039
my mom left for me?

11:08.879 --> 11:11.080
Aren't you managing the household?

11:11.080 --> 11:13.159
Tell us what's going on.

11:14.519 --> 11:15.320
These are...

11:16.519 --> 11:18.080
These are Ying's dowries.

11:18.600 --> 11:19.440
I mixed them.

11:19.720 --> 11:22.399
Li, you must believe me.

11:23.399 --> 11:24.679
While you were away,

11:24.679 --> 11:26.840
we never stopped thinking of you.

11:26.840 --> 11:27.840
Especially your father.

11:27.840 --> 11:30.360
He genuinely looked forward
to your return.

11:31.519 --> 11:32.120
Really?

11:32.679 --> 11:33.399
Of course.

11:33.679 --> 11:34.960
We're keeping a close eye

11:35.919 --> 11:37.240
on the dowry items

11:37.240 --> 11:39.840
your mom left for you.

11:40.919 --> 11:41.919
In the end,

11:42.039 --> 11:44.879
you're the one
who knows how to pull tricks.

11:45.519 --> 11:48.480
No wonder your maiden family
is prospering.

11:53.320 --> 11:55.000
Look at my foolish wife.

11:55.759 --> 11:57.320
You made us a laughingstock.

11:58.559 --> 11:59.360
We found it.

12:01.320 --> 12:02.559
We found it.

12:03.519 --> 12:06.519
Master Wending, Elders.
We found the plaque.

12:08.639 --> 12:09.720
Where was it?

12:10.039 --> 12:11.840
In the pond at the Western Courtyard.

12:13.320 --> 12:14.360
Who put it there?

12:14.679 --> 12:15.399
No idea yet.

12:16.480 --> 12:18.320
Thankfully, Captain Li spotted

12:18.320 --> 12:19.840
a corner of the plaque in the pond.

12:20.159 --> 12:21.279
So we had it retrieved.

12:21.376 --> 12:23.039
(Family of Charity)

12:23.039 --> 12:23.720
Good sign.

12:24.559 --> 12:25.080
Wending.

12:26.559 --> 12:28.879
We found what we've lost.
Everything is fine.

12:29.120 --> 12:30.879
Our "Family of Charity" plaque is found.

12:32.039 --> 12:33.080
What a pity.

12:33.200 --> 12:35.440
It's muddied by the filthy pond water.

12:35.639 --> 12:36.879
Now it's "Family of Filth".

12:37.720 --> 12:39.279
Wash it well

12:39.279 --> 12:41.360
and hang it as soon as possible.

12:41.360 --> 12:42.016
Yes, Master.

12:42.279 --> 12:42.960
You may leave.

12:43.480 --> 12:44.679
Thank goodness we found it.

12:44.679 --> 12:45.639
Clean it well.

12:46.240 --> 12:47.679
Especially "Charity".

12:48.279 --> 12:49.080
Li,

12:49.399 --> 12:50.799
we've found the plaque.

12:50.799 --> 12:52.559
Why don't you go back and rest?

12:52.799 --> 12:54.799
I made a mistake amidst the chaos

12:54.840 --> 12:56.960
and almost mixed up
your dowries with Ying's.

12:57.240 --> 13:00.080
Rest assured.
I'll sort them out and put them back.

13:00.360 --> 13:01.360
You're right, Mother.

13:02.120 --> 13:05.120
Luckily, we came across
the mistake today.

13:05.759 --> 13:06.879
Otherwise,

13:07.080 --> 13:09.720
wouldn't that make you
look like a thief one day?

13:11.600 --> 13:15.039
Since Father, Uncles,
and the Elders are here today,

13:15.519 --> 13:17.159
I'd like to discuss something with you.

13:17.679 --> 13:20.039
My mom left a vast amount behind.

13:20.480 --> 13:22.879
Farmlands, property deeds,
gold and silver shops,

13:23.320 --> 13:25.919
antiques, jades, and such,
all exceedingly complex.

13:26.399 --> 13:28.639
Thank you for managing these
on my behalf.

13:29.879 --> 13:31.559
I won't trouble you with it

13:32.159 --> 13:33.559
since I'm back.

13:33.840 --> 13:35.799
Let's make the handover today.

13:37.600 --> 13:38.399
Of course.

13:43.776 --> 13:49.082
(Family of Charity)

13:59.080 --> 14:00.320
I wanted to do it tomorrow,

14:01.480 --> 14:03.440
but I'm worried that if we delay this,

14:04.200 --> 14:05.799
those outsiders might accuse you

14:06.080 --> 14:08.120
of withholding property
that isn't yours.

14:08.480 --> 14:10.080
We can't let such accusations

14:10.240 --> 14:12.720
tarnish your longstanding reputation.

14:13.759 --> 14:16.840
So I should thank you, Li.

14:17.080 --> 14:18.320
No need, Mother.

14:18.840 --> 14:20.559
That would make us seem estranged.

14:21.519 --> 14:23.679
I see you as my own daughter.

14:24.519 --> 14:26.440
Both you and Ying are dear to me

14:26.799 --> 14:28.519
in precisely the same way.

14:30.039 --> 14:32.440
I promise I will be as filial as Ying

14:33.000 --> 14:34.720
to repay your kindness.

14:40.960 --> 14:42.960
My Lady, so many treasures.

14:42.960 --> 14:44.039
You're rich.

14:44.600 --> 14:46.159
This could last you forever.

14:46.759 --> 14:47.759
You're exaggerating.

14:48.279 --> 14:50.159
There will be plenty of uses for money.

14:50.960 --> 14:52.679
Qingyu, have you checked everything?

14:53.039 --> 14:53.960
Yes, My Lady.

14:55.559 --> 14:56.320
Put them away.

14:56.480 --> 14:57.024
Alright.

15:01.080 --> 15:01.960
You must be tired.

15:01.960 --> 15:02.720
Go rest.

15:02.960 --> 15:03.720
- Yes, My Lady.
- Yes, My Lady.

15:07.039 --> 15:08.128
Our lady is formidable.

15:08.128 --> 15:10.399
Yes, we'll have good days ahead of us.

15:16.480 --> 15:18.399
Tao and Xing are still young.

15:18.399 --> 15:19.759
They speak recklessly.

15:20.240 --> 15:21.480
Please don't mind them.

15:23.240 --> 15:25.759
You were younger than them
when you began serving me.

15:26.320 --> 15:28.320
Qingshuang and I
returned to Lishan Mountain,

15:29.159 --> 15:30.360
while you remained.

15:31.759 --> 15:33.879
You've suffered a lot.

15:35.519 --> 15:38.120
You must be tired, My Lady.
Get some rest.

15:38.200 --> 15:39.360
I'll take my leave.

15:55.168 --> 15:55.960
(Qingshuang)

15:55.960 --> 15:58.159
My Lady, you must be so tired.

16:02.519 --> 16:03.200
I'm fine.

16:08.600 --> 16:10.399
Third watch, Zi hour.

16:10.399 --> 16:11.360
(Ye Mansion)

16:11.360 --> 16:12.879
Cold stars fill the sky.

16:14.240 --> 16:16.200
Sleep peacefully. Don't startle.

16:45.240 --> 16:48.159
(Mom, it's been eight years.)

16:48.679 --> 16:51.080
(No one asked how you have been.)

17:00.960 --> 17:01.879
Mom.

17:02.759 --> 17:04.960
Why did you marry Father?

17:05.599 --> 17:07.200
Because I fancied your father.

17:07.720 --> 17:09.000
And did Father like you?

17:10.119 --> 17:11.400
(Xu Wanzhou, Ye Wenhua's first wife)
Of course he did.

17:11.400 --> 17:11.880
(Young Ye Li)

17:11.880 --> 17:13.160
Your father likes me.

17:13.640 --> 17:14.920
And he likes you too.

17:15.680 --> 17:18.000
Tonight, they will send you
back to Lishan Mountain.

17:18.160 --> 17:19.240
From now on,

17:19.519 --> 17:22.119
we sever our ties
and go our separate ways.

17:41.480 --> 17:42.559
Ye Li.

17:45.920 --> 17:46.880
Ye Li.

17:47.279 --> 17:48.200
Call me "Elder Sister".

17:53.519 --> 17:55.000
You had a nice victory today.

17:57.079 --> 17:58.559
All thanks to your help.

17:59.839 --> 18:00.839
Was the pond chilly?

18:03.279 --> 18:06.160
My mom said
your husband-to-be is crippled.

18:06.319 --> 18:08.960
Life won't be easy if you marry him.

18:11.799 --> 18:13.000
Not necessarily.

18:14.599 --> 18:16.759
Aren't you afraid I'll tell everyone?

18:17.359 --> 18:18.039
Would you?

18:19.200 --> 18:21.319
Your mom left you those dowries.

18:21.319 --> 18:22.759
They're yours to begin with.

18:26.480 --> 18:27.960
You can't get to me.

18:28.799 --> 18:29.640
Says who?

18:34.272 --> 18:38.464
(Ye Mansion)

18:51.680 --> 18:52.800
(Master Zhu said)

18:53.600 --> 18:55.079
(my mom was a fool.)

18:56.039 --> 18:57.664
(What was so good about my father?)

18:58.079 --> 19:00.920
(He was utterly worthless
apart from his good looks.)

19:05.000 --> 19:05.680
My Lady.

19:10.039 --> 19:11.459
The dowry chests are locked.

19:11.459 --> 19:12.720
I'll have them moved out.

19:16.480 --> 19:17.319
Come on in.

19:26.160 --> 19:27.400
(Master Zhu was right.)

19:28.200 --> 19:29.759
(My mom was a smart woman,)

19:30.079 --> 19:31.680
(but when it came to men,)

19:31.989 --> 19:33.480
(she had no taste.)

19:33.680 --> 19:34.799
You look stunning.

19:37.799 --> 19:38.400
My Lady.

19:39.279 --> 19:40.720
Prince Ding sent the nuptial verses.

19:42.400 --> 19:42.920
Let's go.

19:44.960 --> 19:46.000
Congratulations.

19:46.759 --> 19:48.000
Two weddings in one day.

19:48.000 --> 19:49.640
That calls for celebration.

19:49.640 --> 19:50.599
Congratulations, Madam.

19:50.599 --> 19:52.640
You are blessed with profound fortune.

19:53.000 --> 19:54.400
(Madam of the Ye family)
Wait...

19:55.039 --> 19:56.559
Who is getting married?

19:57.559 --> 19:58.640
Your granddaughters.

19:59.759 --> 20:01.880
The brides are here.

20:03.119 --> 20:03.720
Come here.

20:04.640 --> 20:05.799
Look at the two brides.

20:07.640 --> 20:09.440
Lady Ying looks stunning.

20:10.440 --> 20:11.359
So pretty.

20:11.799 --> 20:12.960
Lady Li is stunning too.

20:12.960 --> 20:13.640
So beautiful.

20:23.759 --> 20:24.519
- Grandmother.
- Grandmother.

20:27.584 --> 20:28.240
What...?

20:37.200 --> 20:38.440
Wanzhou.

20:40.319 --> 20:42.240
I haven't seen you for a while.

20:43.359 --> 20:44.119
Grandmother.

20:46.759 --> 20:48.400
I am your mother-in-law.

20:48.920 --> 20:51.240
How come you don't even recognize me?

20:51.400 --> 20:52.319
Madam is tired.

20:52.319 --> 20:52.839
I am...

20:52.839 --> 20:54.000
Help Madam back to rest.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.720
I am your mother-in-law.

20:55.720 --> 20:57.920
I have been thinking of you.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.920
Scatter gold and silver

20:59.920 --> 21:01.519
to joy a newfound groom.

21:01.640 --> 21:03.319
Scatter gold and silver

21:03.319 --> 21:05.240
to joy a newfound groom.

21:07.359 --> 21:09.359
Beat the thieves, but greet the guests.

21:09.839 --> 21:12.319
The sisters-in-law
have come to greet the bride.

21:13.720 --> 21:15.480
Where do paired candles lead to?

21:15.920 --> 21:18.400
Why does the goose crane its neck?

21:18.559 --> 21:20.359
Brilliant light illuminates the path.

21:20.359 --> 21:20.720
(Mo Jingli, Prince Li)

21:20.720 --> 21:23.200
Ride gracefully
into the hall of splendor.

21:24.240 --> 21:26.960
Why are we stuck here?
Where's the messenger we sent?

21:27.480 --> 21:29.200
He should be back soon.

21:29.344 --> 21:31.599
(Mo Wuyou, Prince Ding's nephew)
What if we miss the auspicious hour?

21:33.640 --> 21:34.759
Ask them to step aside.

21:34.759 --> 21:36.279
They can't block the road.

21:36.599 --> 21:37.240
Right?

21:37.519 --> 21:39.599
Just a second.
I'll report this to the master.

21:40.160 --> 21:43.079
The bride proceeds from stately halls.

21:43.079 --> 21:45.839
Scatter gold and silver
to joy a newfound groom.

21:45.839 --> 21:47.000
Scatter gold and silver...

21:47.000 --> 21:47.799
Make way, please.

21:48.544 --> 21:49.240
Master Wenhua.

21:50.752 --> 21:51.400
Master Wenhua.

21:51.720 --> 21:53.920
Both wedding processions have arrived.

21:54.240 --> 21:55.319
Let's get started.

21:55.519 --> 21:58.079
But Prince Li's wedding procession
blocked the alley,

21:58.160 --> 21:59.359
making it inaccessible

21:59.359 --> 22:00.759
for Prince Ding's procession.

22:01.400 --> 22:02.200
Master Wenhua.

22:02.559 --> 22:04.559
Prince Ding inquires about the plan.

22:05.759 --> 22:06.368
Well...

22:06.368 --> 22:07.136
Wenhua.

22:08.640 --> 22:10.240
The auspicious hour has arrived.

22:10.240 --> 22:13.400
Since Prince Li's carriage
is at the entrance,

22:13.400 --> 22:14.440
I suggest

22:15.039 --> 22:17.519
we let Ying set about first.

22:18.079 --> 22:18.920
What about Li?

22:19.319 --> 22:21.680
Wenhua, Li is also your daughter.

22:22.559 --> 22:24.119
Don't tell me you agree with Wending.

22:24.640 --> 22:25.680
No way.

22:26.039 --> 22:27.136
Li will go first.

22:27.529 --> 22:29.519
Lay the felt mat

22:29.519 --> 22:31.200
to keep her feet off the ground.

22:31.200 --> 22:32.559
It's not against custom.

22:33.440 --> 22:35.200
You want Li to walk out by herself?

22:35.799 --> 22:38.759
I've heard that fish beneath the ice

22:38.759 --> 22:41.279
have to breach a crack open
to grasp a breath.

22:42.119 --> 22:44.160
Li, you must remember

22:44.559 --> 22:47.960
the dignity your father sees fit
to grant you today.

22:48.279 --> 22:50.599
Nobody would think you're mute
if you stay quiet.

22:51.799 --> 22:54.200
The auspicious hour is upon us.

22:59.279 --> 23:01.880
The brides shall kneel in gratitude

23:02.039 --> 23:05.079
for their parents' toil in raising them.

23:22.839 --> 23:24.599
Honor and heed them.

23:25.000 --> 23:27.559
Never disobey
your father- and mother-in-law.

23:28.119 --> 23:30.079
- I won't forget your teachings.
- I won't forget your teachings.

23:31.776 --> 23:33.319
Endeavor and revere.

23:33.759 --> 23:36.519
Never transgress the proprieties
expected of a woman.

23:37.279 --> 23:39.200
I won't forget your teachings.

23:39.640 --> 23:41.880
The mother shall
adjust the bride's garments.

24:07.920 --> 24:10.480
(The towering Lishan Mountain
rises into the sky.)

24:11.519 --> 24:14.400
(The mighty Lishui River
flows broad and deep.)

24:15.400 --> 24:16.799
(I traveled alone)

24:17.440 --> 24:19.079
(when I left the capital back then,)

24:19.799 --> 24:21.480
(and returned alone two months ago.)

24:21.920 --> 24:23.279
(I could do it before.)

24:23.440 --> 24:26.400
(I can do it again.)

24:27.279 --> 24:27.840
Father.

24:29.599 --> 24:30.319
I am leaving.

25:04.839 --> 25:07.584
Chopsticks scattered. All ills undone.

25:07.584 --> 25:10.559
Gate thrown wide. All blessings come.

25:12.000 --> 25:13.480
(The late emperor)

25:14.119 --> 25:15.720
(betrothed me to Prince Li.)

25:16.240 --> 25:17.960
(I saw it as my way down the mountain.)

25:18.359 --> 25:19.960
(But Prince Li broke his word.)

25:19.960 --> 25:22.440
(He begged the Empress Dowager
for Ye Ying instead.)

25:23.319 --> 25:24.720
(She agreed,)

25:25.160 --> 25:26.920
(but then betrothed me to Prince Ding.)

25:27.640 --> 25:29.039
(Her intentions remain unclear.)

25:30.039 --> 25:31.200
(But regardless,)

25:32.160 --> 25:33.440
(I'm off the mountain.)

26:03.552 --> 26:05.408
(Qingbao)

26:13.824 --> 26:18.176
(Suixin, Prince Li's Chief Clerk)

26:21.240 --> 26:23.960
Chopsticks scattered. All ills undone.

26:23.960 --> 26:26.960
Gate thrown wide. All blessings come.

26:28.279 --> 26:28.920
Young Lord.

26:36.200 --> 26:36.880
Aunt.

26:37.680 --> 26:38.680
I am Mo Wuyou.

26:39.319 --> 26:41.640
I am here on behalf of my uncle,
Prince Ding.

26:42.319 --> 26:43.480
My uncle is unwell.

26:43.839 --> 26:46.559
Therefore, we have omitted
some of the formalities.

26:47.799 --> 26:49.039
I hope you will forgive us.

26:51.559 --> 26:52.920
Please step into the carriage.

27:10.560 --> 27:15.264
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

27:27.880 --> 27:29.839
Mind your steps, dear bride.

27:40.720 --> 27:41.720
Pass the felt mat.

27:48.352 --> 27:51.808
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

27:59.400 --> 28:01.160
Turn the mat to welcome offspring.

28:01.759 --> 28:03.519
Pass the bag to start a line of heirs.

28:04.480 --> 28:06.039
Grain and beans scattered once.

28:06.640 --> 28:08.440
Ward off evil and disasters.

28:08.640 --> 28:10.319
Grain and beans scattered twice.

28:10.640 --> 28:12.519
Bring peace to the household.

28:21.408 --> 28:24.224
(Wen Ran, Prince Ding's
eldest sister-in-law)

28:32.279 --> 28:34.720
Ms. Wen, where is His Highness?

28:34.839 --> 28:36.160
He mustn't be late.

28:37.240 --> 28:39.400
He should be here soon.
Give him a second.

29:02.559 --> 29:04.680
Will we miss the auspicious hour?

29:04.960 --> 29:06.440
It has long since passed.

29:08.279 --> 29:10.720
It's so late.
Will His Highness even come?

29:12.160 --> 29:13.000
His Highness...

29:13.599 --> 29:15.519
His Highness is detained
by pressing matters.

29:16.759 --> 29:18.000
No matter what,

29:18.559 --> 29:20.039
he should have arrived by now.

29:20.440 --> 29:21.279
Could it be that

29:21.559 --> 29:23.839
Prince Ding is displeased
with the Empress Dowager's

29:23.839 --> 29:24.720
marriage arrangement?

29:25.240 --> 29:26.368
That is not the case.

29:26.368 --> 29:27.440
Go take a look.

29:27.440 --> 29:28.039
Wait.

29:31.160 --> 29:32.960
Where is His Highness?

29:33.920 --> 29:35.920
In his study, I believe.

29:36.960 --> 29:39.079
Let me fetch him in person.

29:48.039 --> 29:50.200
Your Highness.

29:50.200 --> 29:50.990
Your Highness.

29:50.990 --> 29:53.559
I am Prince Ding's steward.
My surname is Cui.

29:53.599 --> 29:54.920
May I show you the way?

30:02.559 --> 30:03.359
And that is...?

30:04.079 --> 30:06.319
That is Director Lv Cheng
of the Bureau of Astronomy.

30:06.319 --> 30:09.039
The Empress Dowager sent him
to aid His Highness' cultivation.

30:09.960 --> 30:11.799
Your Highness, we must show respect.

30:13.319 --> 30:14.160
Cultivation?

30:23.960 --> 30:24.759
Stop there.

30:27.200 --> 30:28.039
Who are you?

30:28.880 --> 30:29.960
I am the Princess Consort.

30:30.304 --> 30:32.200
(Lv Cheng,
Director of the Bureau of Astronomy)

30:32.200 --> 30:34.240
Prince Ding is occupied
with urgent matters.

30:35.960 --> 30:37.920
Am I not even allowed to see him?

30:41.984 --> 30:45.472
(Day and Night Diligence)

31:09.696 --> 31:13.184
(Mo Xiuyao, Prince Ding)

31:25.960 --> 31:26.759
Your Highness.

31:28.240 --> 31:29.960
My apologies. I will pick them up.

32:01.720 --> 32:02.519
Copying sutras?

32:03.880 --> 32:06.400
You have to do this
even on your wedding day?

32:13.319 --> 32:14.079
What's wrong?

32:15.000 --> 32:15.759
Nothing.

32:17.359 --> 32:20.240
I think I finally understand my mom.

32:21.680 --> 32:24.359
Mo Xiuyao, I am Ye Li.

32:24.799 --> 32:25.960
I'm here to marry you.

32:27.160 --> 32:29.599
It's our first meeting.
Let me treat you to a dessert.

32:57.319 --> 32:58.000
No?

32:59.720 --> 33:00.720
Well then, let's go.

33:01.839 --> 33:02.640
Where to?

33:03.799 --> 33:04.759
To the wedding.

33:05.559 --> 33:07.400
Today is our wedding day.

33:07.799 --> 33:09.880
Are you going to
keep copying sutras here?

33:10.440 --> 33:11.960
But I haven't finished yet.

33:12.119 --> 33:13.279
Then do it later.

33:15.559 --> 33:17.839
I will help you once we're back.

33:34.560 --> 33:35.200
Let's go.

33:55.559 --> 33:57.119
Where are you going, Your Highness?

33:59.920 --> 34:01.039
Isn't it obvious?

34:01.799 --> 34:03.759
He hasn't completed
his assignment today.

34:05.279 --> 34:07.400
Getting married
is one of life's biggest events.

34:07.640 --> 34:09.079
Does an assignment matter more?

34:09.719 --> 34:11.079
Your Highness, you may not know.

34:11.280 --> 34:13.079
The Bureau of Astronomy reported

34:13.480 --> 34:15.480
that the excessive bloodshed
in this mansion

34:15.559 --> 34:16.840
has offended the deities.

34:17.079 --> 34:18.639
His Highness's unhealing leg ailment,

34:18.760 --> 34:20.519
Ms. Wen's chronic illness,

34:20.960 --> 34:23.119
and Young Lord's incorrigible behavior.

34:23.119 --> 34:24.599
These are divine punishments.

34:26.800 --> 34:28.320
Out of compassion,

34:29.079 --> 34:31.880
the Empress Dowager
ordered me to divine a remedy.

34:32.880 --> 34:34.880
Only if the head of the household

34:34.880 --> 34:37.159
copies the sutras and recites them daily

34:37.679 --> 34:39.719
can this calamity be resolved.

34:40.079 --> 34:41.679
Does he have to do it now?

34:42.039 --> 34:43.159
Can't we rearrange?

34:44.639 --> 34:47.880
I'm only following Her Majesty's order.

34:48.519 --> 34:50.079
I don't make rearrangements.

34:50.719 --> 34:51.559
I see.

34:52.480 --> 34:53.320
Steward Cui.

34:53.599 --> 34:54.119
Here.

34:54.119 --> 34:56.352
Prepare the carriage.
I'm returning to Lishan Mountain.

34:58.280 --> 34:59.519
What do you mean by this?

35:01.039 --> 35:03.920
By the Empress Dowager's decree,
I came to marry Prince Ding.

35:04.159 --> 35:05.719
But the auspicious hour has passed.

35:05.880 --> 35:07.880
You still refuse to let him go.

35:08.280 --> 35:10.440
It seems the wedding won't proceed.

35:10.599 --> 35:11.800
In that case,

35:12.000 --> 35:13.440
why would I stay here?

35:13.870 --> 35:15.119
I'd better head back.

35:15.199 --> 35:17.000
But I'm afraid you will have to

35:17.119 --> 35:19.360
go to the Anqing Palace
for further instructions.

35:29.360 --> 35:32.480
I'm merely carrying out orders.

35:33.760 --> 35:36.199
I understand.
You've worked hard, Lord Lv.

35:47.760 --> 35:48.760
Steward Cui.

35:48.760 --> 35:49.280
Here.

35:49.519 --> 35:50.240
Let's go.

35:58.760 --> 35:59.440
You're Ye Li?

36:00.039 --> 36:00.559
Yes.

36:01.360 --> 36:02.559
You're from Lishan Academy?

36:02.639 --> 36:03.168
Yes.

36:06.400 --> 36:07.599
I heard you were

36:08.280 --> 36:09.599
betrothed to Prince Li.

36:11.480 --> 36:13.039
You are very well-informed.

36:16.440 --> 36:19.079
Prince Li is handsome
and gentle-mannered,

36:19.719 --> 36:22.280
with exceptional skills in the arts.

36:23.760 --> 36:26.280
He's the ideal husband
for the noble ladies in the capital.

36:27.440 --> 36:30.079
But I sit in a wheelchair
due to my impaired legs.

36:31.159 --> 36:33.400
My family carries the burden
of past crimes.

36:33.400 --> 36:34.519
Its glory has faded.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.320
You've gone from Prince Li's bride

36:38.079 --> 36:39.760
to my wife.

36:40.639 --> 36:41.679
How do you feel?

36:43.840 --> 36:45.559
Prince Li has become so popular now?

36:46.079 --> 36:47.519
No wonder he broke it off.

36:48.239 --> 36:50.239
I didn't know
because I had been in seclusion.

36:52.360 --> 36:53.360
But Your Highness,

36:53.960 --> 36:56.039
your family may have lost its splendor.

36:56.079 --> 36:58.400
The Lishan Academy
is a fading glory too.

36:58.880 --> 37:00.320
Our marriage is like

37:00.719 --> 37:02.599
withered lotuses beside dead willows

37:02.800 --> 37:04.280
and dying grass under winter crows.

37:04.320 --> 37:05.800
A perfect match.

37:06.360 --> 37:07.599
Let's not point any fingers.

37:08.719 --> 37:10.920
The auspicious hour has passed.
We should hurry up.

37:18.960 --> 37:20.639
Ms. Wen, they are here.

37:23.519 --> 37:24.239
Xiuyao.

37:24.519 --> 37:25.320
Sorry, we're late.

37:25.599 --> 37:27.559
No problem. I'm glad you made it.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.760
Your Highness,
it's time for the ceremony.

37:38.239 --> 37:39.519
Bow to the mirror.

37:43.039 --> 37:45.559
Henceforth united as one
before the mirror.

37:45.800 --> 37:48.639
Shared devotion
dispels all hidden evils.

37:51.679 --> 37:53.559
Bind the sash and adjust the attire.

37:53.760 --> 37:56.079
Hold the red silk
and enter the bridal chamber.

38:42.079 --> 38:43.392
Are you hungry, Your Highness?

38:44.639 --> 38:45.880
Want to eat something?

38:48.760 --> 38:51.239
Or have some wine?

38:57.360 --> 38:58.039
What is that?

39:00.519 --> 39:01.199
Curious?

39:03.039 --> 39:05.880
The wedding night
is much easier for common folks.

39:07.719 --> 39:09.960
The natural bond
between man and woman comes easily.

39:10.960 --> 39:12.800
But an impaired man needs some help

39:13.679 --> 39:15.119
on the wedding night.

39:17.599 --> 39:18.760
Want to try it?

39:40.719 --> 39:42.800
These are the dowries
my mom left for me.

39:44.199 --> 39:45.440
What are you doing?

39:46.719 --> 39:47.920
I want to find you a gift.

39:48.519 --> 39:49.400
A gift?

39:51.159 --> 39:51.960
Why?

39:54.880 --> 39:56.320
Because I'm grateful.

40:01.719 --> 40:02.800
As you know,

40:03.679 --> 40:05.159
I was betrothed to Prince Li.

40:06.039 --> 40:08.400
I thought he would marry me
when the time came,

40:09.159 --> 40:10.599
and I would leave the mountain.

40:11.960 --> 40:14.280
But he broke off the engagement.

40:14.840 --> 40:15.800
I understand.

40:16.840 --> 40:19.679
Nowadays, no one wants anything
to do with Lishan.

40:21.239 --> 40:22.719
But you're willing to marry me

40:23.159 --> 40:24.639
and get me off the mountain.

40:25.000 --> 40:25.960
So I'm grateful.

40:32.039 --> 40:32.599
Come here.

40:59.119 --> 41:01.079
Your Highness, what's wrong?

41:03.320 --> 41:04.320
Are you hurting?

41:05.599 --> 41:06.400
Your Highness?

41:18.599 --> 41:19.159
Scared?

41:27.119 --> 41:27.760
Jin.

41:28.199 --> 41:28.719
Here.

41:42.480 --> 41:44.960
People from Lishan Academy
are said to be clever.

41:45.639 --> 41:46.400
But Ye Li.

41:47.280 --> 41:48.599
Rein in your cleverness.

41:50.239 --> 41:51.679
This place is no haven.

41:52.639 --> 41:55.320
And I'm not interested in this marriage.

41:57.480 --> 41:58.240
If you wish,

41:59.040 --> 42:00.599
we could leave each other in peace.

42:01.840 --> 42:02.880
If not,

42:03.880 --> 42:04.920
wait a year or so,

42:05.440 --> 42:06.880
and I'll grant you a divorce.

42:07.840 --> 42:09.679
We can part ways peacefully. Agreed?

42:27.040 --> 42:33.248
(Tuisi Pavilion)

42:33.248 --> 42:36.640
(Preview)

42:36.920 --> 42:38.199
(Mo Xiuyao.)

42:38.840 --> 42:40.480
(What my mom owes your family,)

42:40.960 --> 42:42.239
(I'll pay on her behalf.)

42:43.280 --> 42:44.440
As you know,

42:44.440 --> 42:46.280
the family has received
divine punishments.

42:47.360 --> 42:49.239
I heard you are from the south.

42:49.440 --> 42:50.760
How long have you been here?

42:51.360 --> 42:51.920
Three years.

42:52.400 --> 42:53.440
Let me read your fortune.

42:54.079 --> 42:56.280
Mo Xiuyao, do you want to have a try?

42:57.360 --> 42:58.360
Please leave, Ye Li.

42:58.760 --> 42:59.760
I don't need you.

43:02.760 --> 43:03.679
I've mastered it too.

43:04.320 --> 43:04.920
Is it similar?

43:11.856 --> 43:18.448
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:22.032 --> 43:28.176
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:30.384 --> 43:33.616
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:33.840 --> 43:39.856
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:40.176 --> 43:43.600
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:43.664 --> 43:50.224
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:51.280 --> 43:55.216
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:55.216 --> 44:00.912
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:01.424 --> 44:10.032
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:10.928 --> 44:16.432
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:16.432 --> 44:21.936
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:22.000 --> 44:26.064
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:26.352 --> 44:31.576
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:32.176 --> 44:35.888
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:35.920 --> 44:41.584
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:42.352 --> 44:50.320
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:51.728 --> 44:56.976
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

44:57.232 --> 45:03.136
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:03.136 --> 45:07.256
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:07.472 --> 45:12.208
♪Unbound by form♪

45:13.424 --> 45:17.696
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:17.936 --> 45:23.376
♪Unbound by form♪
